## 2026-05-15 ‚Äî MASTRA-049 session 6: GEO_PATTERNS refactor + Supabase quota guard + env.example docs

**Task:** P1 Maps Grounding enablement gates ‚Äî structured GEO_PATTERNS (English-only), Supabase-persisted daily quota counter, `.env.example` `VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_MAP_ID` documentation
**Score: 95/100** (was 92, +3 ‚Äî Item 8 Maps Grounding 7‚Üí9/10)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| `supabase/functions/ai-chat/index.ts` | **REFACTOR** ‚Äî `groundWithMaps`: replaced single broad venue-type regex with 6-pattern `GEO_PATTERNS` array targeting proximity/live-state queries only; added `serviceClient: SupabaseClientType` param; added Supabase-persisted daily quota guard (reads/writes `grounding_quota_log`); call site updated to pass `getServiceClient()` |
| `src/lib/places-enrichment-compliance.test.ts` | **+9 tests** ‚Äî `groundWithMaps` quota guard compliance: serviceClient param, GEO_PATTERNS array, proximity keywords ("near", "close to", "walking distance"), live-state keywords ("open now", "currently open"), quota_log read-before-API, `MAPS_GROUNDING_DAILY_LIMIT` env, fire-and-forget increment, non-fatal catch |
| `.env.example` | **+14 lines** ‚Äî `VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_MAP_ID` documented with step-by-step instructions for creating a Map ID in Cloud Console and setting it in Vercel |
| `tasks/mastra/audit/04-production-readiness-checklist.md` | Score 92 ‚Üí 95; Item 8 (Maps Grounding) 7‚Üí9; Item 10 count 198‚Üí207; fix priority table P1 code items marked ‚úÖ DONE |
| `changelog` | This entry |

**What changed in `groundWithMaps`:**

| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| Single broad regex ‚Äî fired on "restaurant", "eat", "dining", any venue word | 6-pattern array ‚Äî fires only on proximity/live-state/navigation queries |
| In-memory counter ‚Äî resets on every cold start | Supabase `grounding_quota_log` ‚Äî survives restarts |
| No `serviceClient` param ‚Äî no DB access | `serviceClient: SupabaseClientType` ‚Äî reads quota before call, writes after |
| No kill switch ‚Äî 500/day hard-coded | `MAPS_GROUNDING_DAILY_LIMIT` env var ‚Äî ops can set to 0 as a kill switch |

**Tests:** 207/207 ¬∑ **Lint:** 0 errors ¬∑ **Build:** exit 0 (6.5s) ¬∑ **Deno check ai-chat:** exit 0

**Remaining user actions before `MDEAI_MAPS_GROUNDING=true` is safe to enable:**
1. `git push origin main` (30+ commits pending)
2. Create Map ID at console.cloud.google.com ‚Üí set `VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_MAP_ID` in Vercel
3. Set `MDEAI_MAPS_GROUNDING=true` in Supabase Edge Function secrets
