## 2026-05-10 ‚Äî VDB-01: Hybrid FTS + Semantic Search (branch `chore/claude-audit-tools`, ai-search v47)

Hybrid search is live. Neighbourhood queries ("El Poblado apartment") now hit FTS first ‚Äî exact text matches surface at relevanceScore=1.0 ‚Äî while vibe queries ("quiet place for remote work") fall back to pure semantic. Both paths go through the same 3 RPCs; latency unchanged.

### What shipped

**`fts_content` generated columns.** `apartments`, `events`, `restaurants` each gained a `tsvector GENERATED ALWAYS AS ... STORED` column using Spanish text config. Postgres maintains them automatically on every INSERT/UPDATE. Two immutable wrappers (`fts_spanish`, `fts_array_to_text`) were required because Supabase's Postgres marks `regconfigin` and `array_to_string` as STABLE, which blocks GENERATED columns from direct calls.

**GIN indexes.** `apartments_fts_idx`, `events_fts_idx`, `restaurants_fts_idx` ‚Äî fast `@@` operator queries with no seq-scan.

**3 hybrid RPCs (RRF scoring).** `hybrid_search_listings`, `hybrid_search_events`, `hybrid_search_restaurants` merge BM25 (`ts_rank_cd`) and cosine similarity rank lists via Reciprocal Rank Fusion: `score = fts_weight/(k+rank_fts) + sem_weight/(k+rank_sem)` (defaults: fts_weight=1.5, sem_weight=1.0, k=60). When FTS returns 0 matches (empty tsquery), only the semantic leg contributes.

**`ai-search` v47.** Replaced `semanticSearch*` calls with `hybridSearch*`. Added `scaleRrf()` helper to map RRF scores [0.01..0.04] ‚Üí [0.6..1.0] so hybrid results always rank above keyword-only fallback results (cars cap at 0.55). Mode label: `"hybrid"`.

### Verification (5/5 tests pass)

```
T1 El Poblado (FTS keyword)   ‚Üí apartment El Poblado  score=1.000  ‚úÖ top result
T2 quiet remote work (vibe)   ‚Üí apartment Provenza     score=0.764  ‚úÖ semantic
T3 Carmen restaurant          ‚Üí restaurant Carmen      score=1.000  ‚úÖ exact + semantic
T4 Poblado Cozy 2BR (regress) ‚Üí apartment Cozy 2BR    score=1.000  ‚úÖ no regression
T5 neighborhood filter        ‚Üí no cars in results               ‚úÖ car exclusion holds
```

